pageProduct.name: Nutra-Life Prostate Complete 60 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Nutra-Life Prostate Complete combines USPlus™ Saw Palmetto with antioxidants Selenium and Zinc plus Vitamin D3. USPlus™ is a high strength, Saw Palmetto extract standardized to deliver 450mg fatty acids per capsule. Saw Palmetto supports prostate health and supports healthy urine output in males when used in traditional western herbal medicine

Suitable For: Prostate health, male reproductive health, healthy testosterone levels, sperm mobility

Size: 60 capsules

KEY FEATURES

• Prostate Health Support when traditionally used in Western herbal medicine
• With high strength USPlus™ Saw Palmetto

Warnings

If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. This product contains selenium which is toxic in high doses. A daily dose of 150micrograms for adults of
selenium from dietary supplements should not be exceeded. WARNING: Contains Zinc which may be dangerous if taken in large amounts or for a long period. Vitamin and mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet.

Ingredients

Each capsule provides:

- Serenoa repens (USPlus™ Saw Palmetto) fruit ext. equiv. fresh 5g, Stand. equiv.
- Fatty acids 450mg
- Selenium (as Selenomethionine) 50µg
- Zinc (as sulfate monohydrate) 15mg
- Colecalciferol (Vit. D3) 5µg
- Encapsulating aids, Colour

USPlusTM is a registered trademark of Valensa International.

Contains: Contains: Animal product, sulfites, soya bean products.

Allergen Free From: Artificial Flavours| Artificial Preservatives| Dairy| Egg| Gluten| Wheat

Directions

RECOMMENDED ADULT DOSAGE: Take 1 capsule daily with food or as directed by your
healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store in a cool, dry place below 30°C.
